tags.name: Camping Los Ocultos
Calilegua National Park
tags.note: Free of charge. No electricity. Toilets relatively clean. Benches and barbeque facilities. NO place for supplies (food or drinkable water) for many kilometers. Nice and quiet. (worldvespa Jun '15)
